    <h1>crosswalk.titles.media</h1>
    <p>A static JSON API mapping film works and persons across IMDb, TMDB, Wikidata, and Letterboxd.</p>
    <p>Full documentation: <a href="https://github.com/titles-media/crosswalk">titles-media/crosswalk</a> on GitHub.</p>

    <h2>Endpoints</h2>

    <h3>Movies</h3>
    <p>Look up a film by internal ID:</p>
    <pre><code>{BASE}/movies/&#123;id&#125;.json</code></pre>
    <p>Look up a film by external ID:</p>
    <pre><code>{BASE}/movies/by_id/&#123;source&#125;/&#123;source_id&#125;.json</code></pre>
    <p>Supported sources: <code>imdb</code>, <code>tmdb</code>, <code>wikidata</code>, <code>letterboxd</code></p>

    <h3>Persons</h3>
    <p>Look up a person by internal ID:</p>
    <pre><code>{BASE}/persons/&#123;id&#125;.json</code></pre>
    <p>Look up a person by external ID:</p>
    <pre><code>{BASE}/persons/by_id/&#123;source&#125;/&#123;source_id&#125;.json</code></pre>
    <p>Supported sources: <code>imdb</code>, <code>tmdb</code>, <code>wikidata</code></p>

    <h2>Examples</h2>
    <pre><code><a href="/movies/by_id/imdb/tt12042730.json">{BASE}/movies/by_id/imdb/tt12042730.json</a>
<a href="/movies/p148c7y3.json">{BASE}/movies/p148c7y3.json</a></code></pre>
    <pre>{JSON.stringify({
      id: "p148c7y3",
      title: "Project Hail Mary",
      year: 2026,
      imdb_id: "tt12042730",
      letterboxd_id: "project-hail-mary",
      tmdb_id: "687163",
      wikidata_id: "Q107105860"
    }, null, 2)}</pre>

    <pre><code><a href="/persons/by_id/imdb/nm0000759.json">{BASE}/persons/by_id/imdb/nm0000759.json</a>
<a href="/persons/pelfst4h.json">{BASE}/persons/pelfst4h.json</a></code></pre>
    <pre>{JSON.stringify({
      id: "pelfst4h",
      name_last: "Anderson",
      name_first: "Paul",
      name_middle: "Thomas",
      birth_year: 1970,
      birth_month: 6,
      birth_day: 26,
      imdb_id: "nm0000759",
      wikidata_id: "Q25132",
      tmdb_id: "4762"
    }, null, 2)}</pre>

